name: The untold stories of Babyboo and Norseman

metadata.name: The War of Rubber Duck
metadata.description:
Norseman's most beloved possession, the rubber duck, has been stolen by Cloaky, the three-headed mask demon.

Norseman has now gone on a wild and violent rampage. He's unleashed his inner monster and transformed his lower body into a horse with a dragon-headed tail. An elf archer baby and a demonoid baby spirit were summoned to him to help him win the battle against Cloaky.

Will Norseman be able to win and take back his precious rubber duck?
